']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Kubernetes Orchestration Guide',\n      body: 'Kubernetes automates deployment, scaling, and management of containerized applications. Key concepts include pods, services, deployments, namespaces, and ingress controllers. Kubernetes provides self-healing, horizontal scaling, rolling updates, and service discovery out of the box.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'devops', 'kubernetes']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Classical Music Appreciation',\n      body: 'Classical music spans centuries from Bach and Handel through Mozart and Beethoven to modern composers. The orchestra typically includes strings, woodwinds, brass, and percussion sections. Major forms include symphonies, concertos, sonatas, and operas. Listening actively to different sections enhances appreciation.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['music', 'classical', 'culture']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Effective Public Speaking',\n      body: 'Great public speakers master preparation, delivery, and audience engagement. Structure talks with a hook, three main points, and a memorable closing. Use pauses for emphasis, vary your tone, maintain eye contact, and use gestures naturally. Practice extensively and seek feedback.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['communication', 'skills', 'career']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Indoor Plant Care Essentials',\n      body: 'Successful indoor gardening requires understanding light, water, and soil needs. Low-light plants like pothos and snake plants are great for beginners. Water when the top inch of soil is dry. Use well-draining potting mix. Fertilize monthly during growing season. Monitor for pests regularly.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['gardening', 'plants', 'home']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'SQLite Full-Text Search Tutorial',\n      body: 'SQLite FTS5 provides powerful full-text search capabilities. Create a virtual table using FTS5, insert content, and query using the MATCH operator. FTS5 supports phrase qu